DTEND;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260302T070000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR
SUMMARY:ONE Thing Block (Protected)
DESCRIPTION:Single highest-leverage action for the day. No phone. No email. One task only.\n\nThis is the non-negotiable block. Everything else fits around it.\n\nBefore starting: confirm today's ONE Thing serves the weekly lead domino.\nAfter completing: log completion in Nightly Reset.
CATEGORIES:ONE Thing,Protected,Deep Work
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT10M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:ONE Thing Block starts in 10 minutes — prepare your single task
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:jaye-os-operator-window-20260302@jayeos
DTSTAMP:20260226T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260302T073000
DTEND;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260302T123000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR
SUMMARY:Operator Window (ThomCo)
DESCRIPTION:Sites, crew, client decisions, supply chain, critical operator work.\n\nKeep it revenue-critical and risk-critical only.\nBatch non-urgent items to the Close Loops window.\n\nRule: if it doesn't affect cash or safety today, it waits.
CATEGORIES:Operator,ThomCo
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT

