DTEND;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260302T170000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR
SUMMARY:Close Loops (30 min)
DESCRIPTION:Invoices, confirmations, email replies, tomorrow setup.\n\nThis is the batched admin window. Everything non-urgent gets handled here.\n\nRule: if you're doing admin outside this window, you're leaking time.
CATEGORIES:Admin,Batching
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT

