DTEND;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260304T124500
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=WE
SUMMARY:Midweek Calibration (30 min)
DESCRIPTION:Quick midweek check-in with yourself.\n\n1. Cash glance — any surprises?\n2. Bottleneck check — is the weekly target on track?\n3. Adjust weekly ONE Thing plan if needed.\n\nThis is calibration, not planning. Keep it under 30 minutes.
CATEGORIES:Calibration,Review
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT

