BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:jaye-os-weekly-calibration-20260306@jayeos
DTSTAMP:20260226T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260306T143000
DTEND;TZID=Australia/Sydney:20260306T153000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=FR
SUMMARY:Weekly Calibration (60 min)
DESCRIPTION:End-of-week review and next-week planning.\n\n1. Review this week's ONE Thing — did it get done?\n2. Review energy trend (Nightly Reset data).\n3. Identify top bottleneck for next week.\n4. Pick next week's ONE Thing using the Focusing Question.\n5. Update Weekly Calibration database in Notion.\n6. Batch any remaining admin.\n\nThis is the most important review of the week.
CATEGORIES:Review,Planning,Weekly
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT15M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Weekly Calibration starts in 15 minutes — gather your data
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

